description:
This is a market on whether the Netflix show, Squid Game, will hold the number one spot on Netflix’s daily U.S. top ten ranking from October 8, 2021 to October 14, 2021 inclusive. The resolution source will be https://flixpatrol.com/top10/netflix/united-states which ranks the top 10 Netflix TV shows in the US. Past top 10 data may be found by appending the date to the aforementioned link, e.g. https://flixpatrol.com/top10/netflix/united-states/2021-09-18/ for September 18. 

The resolution source will be checked at 8 PM ET daily from October 8 to October 14, under "Top 10 TV Shows." If on all of the daily checks "Squid Game" remained #1, the market will resolve to "Yes." If on any of those checks "Squid Game" was not #1, the market will resolve to "No." If the resolution source is unavailable during the checks, another credible resolution source will be chosen such as https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/most-popular/.
